<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَعَقَرُوهَا}</span> ... نَحَرُوهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَادُونَ}</span> ... مُتَجَاوِزُونَ مَا أَبَاحَهُ اللهُ لَكُمْ مِنَ الحَلَالِ إِلَى الحَرَامِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُخْرَجِينَ}</span> ... المَطْرُودِينَ مِنْ بِلَادِنَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْقَالِينَ}</span> ... المُبْغِضِينَ لِعَمَلِكُمْ بُغْضًا شَدِيدًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
