<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَسَاءَ}</span> ... قَبُحَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَصْحَابُ الْأَيْكَةِ}</span> ... أَصْحَابُ الأَرْضِ ذَاتِ الشَّجَرِ المُلْتَفِّ؛ وَهُمْ قَوْمُ شُعَيْبٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٨١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُخْسِرِينَ}</span> ... النَّاقِصِينَ لِحُقُوقِ النَّاسِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
